<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">Activity: A group of contexts within a process 
that can only be entered
by a single causality at a time</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5"> 
Method calls into an activity must acquire a causality-based</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5"> 
lock before being processed</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5" color="#FF0000">Key point:</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5" color="#FF0000">An activity is utilized to 
achieve synchronization among COM+ objects</font></p>

